lated by using the Pitzer equations with the parameter values of Pitzer and Mayorga [J. Phys. Chem. 77 (1973) 2300], and to those calculated by using the extended Hückel equation of Hamer and Wu [J. Phys. Chem. Ref. Data 1 (1972) 1047].},
